  <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mt-6 mb-2">Data submission</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
    You are responsible for the data your applications send to Logister, including any
    personal or sensitive data included in error payloads.
