  </p>

  <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mt-6 mb-2">Contact</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
    For legal questions, contact <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-slate-100 text-slate-800">support@logister.org</code>.
  </p>
</section>
